# Changes

## v1.3
- added columns in course table for new structure
- made assets accessible without authentication

## v1.2.1
- changed ACLs to only restrict file upload, not download
- changed properties in sample courses to match news names in front end

## v1.2
- added editor role, author application

## v1.1.1
- fixed issue where promoted emails weren't correctly sent

## v1.1
- changed ACL to make some API calls publicly available
- changed handling of `FRONTEND_PORT` env variable: it's now omitted when not set instead
of defaulting to `80` in notification templates

## v1.0
First live version for LAYA Iraq.
